<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="Aink118-kilavi">
        ciṟaippuṟamākat talaimakaḷ tōḻikkuc colliyatu; tōḻivāyiṉ maṟutta talaimakaḷ piṉpu talaimakaṉ vantuḻi nikaḻntataṉai avaṭkuk kūṟiyatūumām</p>    <p xml:lang="en">
          Spoken by the heroine to the heroine, [the hero] being at the outer fence. It could also be said to the confidante, that which had happened when the hero came after the heroine, who rejected [him] through the confidante.
            </p>
            </div>  
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink118">
<l>amma vāḻi tōḻi yāṉiṉ</l>
<l>ṟaṟaṉi lāḷaṟ kaṇṭa poḻutiṟ</l>
<l>ciṉavuveṉ ṟakaikkuveṉ ceṉṟaṉeṉ</l>
<l>piṉṉiṉain tiraṅkip peyartan tēṉē</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Oh friend, listen!</l>
<l>Today, at the time when I saw him who is without righteousness,</l>
<l>I went, [thinking] I would be angry, [and that] I would stop [him].</l>
<l>Thinking upon it, pitying [him], I returned.</l>
</lg>
    </div>
